Data Cloud for Financial Services Cloud
Updates to Calculated Insights in Data Cloud and FlexCards in Salesforce to view more customer insights.
Visualize Insights into a Household and its Members
Add the FSCDataCloudShowIncomeExpenses and FSCDataCloudCashFlowByCategory FlexCards to a household account record page. 
Calculate More Customer Insights
Use the Goal Status Calculated Insight in Data Cloud to gain insights into the progress of a financial goal based on the current value, contributions, and target achievement date.
